name: SetUtilsTest
description: Unit tests for various SetUtils operations including difference, disjunction, intersection, union, and more.

test_cases.name: testDifference
test_cases.description: Tests the difference operation between two sets.

test_cases.name: testDisjunction
test_cases.description: Tests the disjunction operation between two sets.

test_cases.name: testEmptyIfNull
test_cases.description: Tests the emptyIfNull operation which returns an empty set if the input set is null.

test_cases.name: testEquals
test_cases.description: Tests the isEqualSet operation which checks if two sets are equal.

test_cases.name: testHashCode
test_cases.description: Tests the hashCodeForSet operation which computes the hash code for a set.

test_cases.name: testHashSet
test_cases.description: Tests the creation of unmodifiable and hash sets using SetUtils.

test_cases.name: testIntersection
test_cases.description: Tests the intersection operation between two sets.

test_cases.name: testNewIdentityHashSet
test_cases.description: Tests the creation of a new identity hash set using SetUtils.

test_cases.name: testpredicatedSet
test_cases.description: Tests the creation of a predicated set using SetUtils.

test_cases.name: testUnion
test_cases.description: Tests the union operation between two sets.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSet
test_cases.description: Tests the creation of unmodifiable sets using SetUtils.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSetWrap
test_cases.description: Tests the wrapping of an existing set into an unmodifiable set using SetUtils.
